HEADWORD: Monochlamydeous
<hw>Mon`o*chla*myd"e*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Mono-</ets> + Gr. <?/, <?/, cloak: cf. F.
